# =============================================================================
# scripts/services.dep — Service dependency declarations
# =============================================================================
#
# Only list services that HAVE dependencies.
# Everything else is auto-discovered from compose.yml files and runs
# alphabetically. Boot order is derived automatically via topological sort.
#
# FORMAT:
#   service -> dep1 dep2 dep3
#
# RULES:
#   - Left side:  the service that needs something before it can start
#   - Right side: one or more space-separated services it depends on
#   - Circular dependencies are detected and reported clearly on every run
#   - Names must match the directory name containing the compose.yml
#
# ADDING A SERVICE WITH NO DEPENDENCIES:
#   Just create the compose.yml anywhere under homelab/. Done.
#   No entry needed here.
#
# ADDING A SERVICE THAT DEPENDS ON OTHERS:
#   myservice -> dep1 dep2
#
# =============================================================================

dns        -> vpn
traefik    -> vpn
open-webui -> ollama
